Introduction

ATTEMPTED SCOTTY'S CANYON WITH RICK KENT AND COMPANY 3-22-09 BY ACCESSING THROUGH ASHFORD CANYON. WE HAD AN EXTREMELY WINDY DAY AND TRIED TO THROW THE ROPES DOWN THE RAPPEL AND THEY KEPT BLOWING BACK UP. SO WE BAILED. AND THEN WE CAME BACK AGAIN 11-22-09 AND COMPLETED SCOTTY'S CANYON - WILL BE POSTING THE BETA I HAVE VERY SOON WITH PHOTOS.
